},
"61": {
&"character": "Erika",
&"id": "61",
&"next_id": "62",
&"text": "A man who's after a heart I see hehe",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"62": {
&"character": "Erika",
&"id": "62",
&"next_id": "63",
&"text": "One day I'd like to be a loving dorm bride 🤭",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"63": {
&"character": "Erika",
&"id": "63",
&"next_id": "64",
&"text": "The sorority's little tradition... a girl chosen to belong to one lucky man",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"64": {
&"character": "Player",
&"id": "64",
&"next_id": "65",
&"text": "What about your boyfriend though?",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"65": {
&"character": "Erika",
&"id": "65",
&"next_id": "66",
&"text": "To be honest, it's a long complicated story but he's actually my fiansay",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"66": {
&"character": "Erika",
&"id": "66",
&"next_id": "67",
&"text": "Is that how you spell it? 🫢",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"67": {
&"character": "Player",
&"id": "67",
&"next_id": "68",
&"text": "You're engaged!?",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"68": {
&"character": "Erika",
&"id": "68",
&"next_id": "69",
&"text": "It's not by choice darling 🥺",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"69": {
&"character": "Erika",
&"id": "69",
&"next_id": "70",
&"text": "I want to live with my lover, not in an arranged relationship 🤭",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"7": {
&"character": "Erika",
&"id": "7",
&"next_id": "8",
&"text": "Hi handsome 💋",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"70": {
&"character": "Erika",
&"id": "70",
&"next_id": "71",
&"text": "How would you feel if you were forced into a relationship? 🥺",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"71": {
&"character": "Erika",
&"id": "71",
&"next_id": "72",
&"text": "Anyway, under Jessica that relationship doesn't mean anything",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"72": {
&"character": "Erika",
&"id": "72",
&"next_id": "73",
&"text": "And being a dorm bride might be the only way I'll get to have something real, that I can accept on my own terms",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"73": {
&"character": "Erika",
&"id": "73",
&"next_id": "74",
&"text": "So I feel a little safer in the Sorority 🤗",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"74": {
&"character": "Player",
&"id": "74",
&"next_id": "75",
&"text": "I see 😕",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"75": {
&"character": "Erika",
&"id": "75",
&"next_id": "76",
&"text": "But I don't want to go off topic",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"76": {
&"character": "Erika",
&"id": "76",
&"next_id": "77",
&"text": "Wouldn't you say we're all still a little \"flexible\"? 😘",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"77": {
&"character": "Player",
&"id": "77",
&"next_id": "78",
&"text": "I guess 😅",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"78": {
&"character": "Erika",
&"id": "78",
&"next_id": "79",
&"text": "I've been with a lot of guys honey",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"79": {
&"character": "Erika",
&"id": "79",
&"next_id": "80",
&"text": "But I'm going to use everything I've learned for the one that picks me to be theirs 🥰",
