raw_text = "~ start
##8:27pm
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Erika: Mmmh well if it isn't the boy who called my name today 🥰
Erika: Out of all the girls you could've chosen too
Erika: Well, maybe between just me and Nina today but all the same
Player: Hey Erika
Erika: Hi handsome 💋
Erika: You really that interested in little old me? ☺️
- I picked you, didn't I?
	Player: I picked you, didn't I?
	Erika: Mhmm 🥰 you certainly did
	Erika: Don't let it go to your pretty head too fast though
- You stood out to me
	Player: You stood out to me
	Erika: Careful sugar 😘 say things like that and I might start liking you
Erika: So what's the big idea with your girlfriend anyway 🤭
Erika: There's just a bit of gossip about you
Player: Really? Like what?
Erika: Y'know, the usual girl talk hehe
Erika: About the new adorable couple
Player: What does that mean?
Erika: Oh nevermind that for now
Erika: Tell me hansome
Erika: handsome*
Erika: img: erika/15
Erika: Does she know you're texting all this right now? 🤭
- No... 😳 [#yellowheart]
	set Story.yellow_heart += 1
	Player: No... 😳
	Erika: Ooh 🤭 a little dangerous then, I do like that
	Erika: I've got a boy waiting for me too
	Erika: But here we are
	Player: Here we are
- I'm just here to plan the date 😅
	Player: I'm just here to plan the date 😅
	Erika: So responsible 🥰 we'll see how long that lasts
Erika: Relax sugar, I'm not trying to steal you from her
Player: Sure sounds like it though 😅
Erika: That's not my style at all 😌
Erika: In fact, I want quite the opposite 🥰
Player: The opposite? What does that mean
Erika: I guess a pure hearted cutie like you wouldn't really see it yet 🤭
Erika: I'm a fair bit older than your cute little batch of cubs y'know
Player: Really?
Erika: Mhmm.. I'm in Jessica's batch hehe
Erika: But I'm not very smart 😋
Erika: Would it be okay if I brought some of my homework and you help me out 😚
- Of course!
	Player: Of course!
	Erika: Oh my hero 🥺
- I guess 😅
	Player: I guess 😅
	Erika: Thank you sweetie 🥰
Erika: You're a life safer
Erika: saver* oopsie
Erika: Tell me handsome, are you planning to take a dorm bride for yourself one day? 🥰
- Of course [#yellowheart]
	set Story.yellow_heart += 1
	set Story.flag = \"ErikasSecret\"
	Player: Of course
	Erika: A man who's after a heart I see hehe
	Erika: One day I'd like to be a loving dorm bride 🤭
	Erika: The sorority's little tradition... a girl chosen to belong to one lucky man
	Player: What about your boyfriend though?
	Erika: To be honest, it's a long complicated story but he's actually my fiansay
	Erika: Is that how you spell it? 🫢
	Player: You're engaged!?
	Erika: It's not by choice darling 🥺
	Erika: I want to live with my lover, not in an arranged relationship 🤭
	Erika: How would you feel if you were forced into a relationship? 🥺
	Erika: Anyway, under Jessica that relationship doesn't mean anything
	Erika: And being a dorm bride might be the only way I'll get to have something real, that I can accept on my own terms
	Erika: So I feel a little safer in the Sorority 🤗
	Player: I see 😕
	Erika: But I don't want to go off topic
	Erika: Wouldn't you say we're all still a little \"flexible\"? 😘
	Player: I guess 😅
	Erika: I've been with a lot of guys honey
	Erika: But I'm going to use everything I've learned for the one that picks me to be theirs 🥰
	Erika: And your profile picture looks awfully handsome right now ☺️
	Erika: img: erika/16
	Erika: Don't you think our skin would look nice against each other?
	Player: I-I guess..
	Erika: Maybe tipsy ol Erika said a little too much hehe
- I'm not sure exactly
	Player: I'm not sure exactly
	Erika: Really?
	Erika: I suppose it might be a bit early for you to process all that information
Erika: Anyway 🥰 we really should talk about Saturdays date
Erika: Since all expenses are paid for, let's go somewhere they'll regret 😉
Player: Sounds fun, where did you have in mind?
Erika: Somewhere special for sure 🤭
Erika: You'll find out soon enough
Player: Sounds good to me
Erika: Ugh thinking about how it'll be so tight and snug, I'm already a little wet
Player: Oh uhm 😄 ..
- I can't wait
	Player: I can't wait
	Erika: Mmmh good 🥰 neither can I, honestly
- I'll be there
	Player: I'll be there
	Erika: He plays it cool 😏 we'll have to fix that on Saturday
Erika: But don't you get any naughty thoughts. No sex, remember? 🥰
Player: I didn't even.. huh? 😆
Erika: 🥰
if Story.yellow_heart >= 4:
	Erika: I'll leave you with a little something to think about until then 😘
	Erika: img: erika/17
	Erika: That's just the start sugar 🤭
	Erika: Be a good boy and dream of me okay?
- Goodnight Erika
	Player: Goodnight Erika 😊
	Erika: Goodnight my handsome date 💋
- You're trouble 😅
	Player: You're trouble 😅
	Erika: delete: Save your compliments for when you take me 🫦
	Erika: I mean save it for when we go on our date... whoopsie 🥰
	Player: Goodnight Erika 😊
	Erika: Goodnight my handsome date 💋
=> END"
